#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/introduction/otrs.xml:210 en/content/introduction/otrs.xml:580
#: en/content/introduction/otrs.xml:631
msgid "Productivity"
msgstr "Produktivität"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/introduction/otrs.xml:214
msgid ""
"Implemented proper time zone support. Time zones can be configured system "
"wide and also on a per-user basis."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/introduction/otrs.xml:218
msgid "Improvements to ticket handling"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/introduction/otrs.xml:221
msgid ""
"Added possibility to store unfinished ticket forms as drafts for later reuse."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/introduction/otrs.xml:225
msgid ""
"Completely revamped ticket zoom screen, with a fresh new design with accent "
"on content. User avatars have been introduced as a visual aid for easier "
"identification of the article sender. Article display settings are now "
"displayed in a settings dialog."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/introduction/otrs.xml:230
msgid ""
"Dropped dubious and somewhat confusing article types, and introduced the "
"concept of communication channels as source for ticket articles (e.g. Email, "
"Phone, Chat, etc). Customer visibility of articles can now be determined by "
"a simple check-box."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/introduction/otrs.xml:234
msgid "Improved AgentTicketHistory screen usability."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/introduction/otrs.xml:238
msgid ""
"Merged the add-on module OTRSAdvancedTicketSplit. Now it's possible to "
"select to which kind of ticket an article should be split: phone (default), "
"email or process ticket. For process tickets, additional selection of "
"specific process will be provided. However, only those fields which are "
"configured in the first activity dialog will be adopted from original ticket."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/introduction/otrs.xml:243
msgid ""
"Added support for ticket number and title search in ticket merge and bulk "
"screens. Auto-complete list can be used to populate the ticket number field "
"with a single click, therefore speeding up the process and limiting room for "
"error. In the ticket merge screen, there is also a CustomeriD search filter "
"option, which will limit the results to tickets belonging to the same "
"customer company as the source ticket."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/introduction/otrs.xml:247
msgid "Split last sender and ticket title columns in ticket overviews."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/introduction/otrs.xml:251
msgid ""
"It's now possible to access all supported article actions directly from "
"large ticket overview screen."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/introduction/otrs.xml:255
msgid ""
"It is now possible to delete linked objects directly from the zoom view."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/introduction/otrs.xml:258
msgid "Ticket search and statistic can now filter for pending until time."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/introduction/otrs.xml:262
msgid ""
"Added possibility to restrict zoom and print screens in the customer "
"interface by using ACLs."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/introduction/otrs.xml:266
msgid ""
"The used search template is now shown on the ticket search result screen."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/introduction/otrs.xml:270
msgid ""
"Added possibility to automatically lock new tickets to the agent who creates "
"them."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/introduction/otrs.xml:275
msgid ""
"Added possibility to send notifications to the agent who created a ticket, "
"thanks to Dian Tong Software."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/introduction/otrs.xml:280
msgid ""
"Added new recipient notification groups 'AllRecipientsFirstArticle' and "
"'AllRecipientsLastArticle'."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/introduction/otrs.xml:285
msgid ""
"Make it possible to configure which ticket state types to show striked "
"through in the linked objects table, thanks to Renée Bäcker."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/introduction/otrs.xml:290
msgid ""
"Made possible to define ServiceIDs and SLAIDs as default shown ticket search "
"attributes, thanks to Paweł Bogusławski."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/introduction/otrs.xml:295
msgid ""
"Merged the add-on module OTRSTicketCloseRedirect. It is now possible by a "
"new SysConfig setting to stay in Ticket Zoom after an action that closes the "
"ticket instead of been redirected to the last overview screen or dashboard. "
"This is now controlled by the new SysConfig setting \"Ticket::Frontend::"
"RedirectAfterCloseDisabled\"."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/introduction/otrs.xml:300
msgid ""
"Merged the add-on module OTRSUserDefaultQueue, With a new SysConfig setting "
"now it is possible to pre-select a queue to create a ticket in the New "
"Phone, Email and Process ticket screens."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/introduction/otrs.xml:307
msgid ""
"Merged the add-on module OTRSAppointmentCalendar. Now OTRS provides a "
"calendar implementation that allows agents to manage and display multiple "
"calendars and their appointments."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/introduction/otrs.xml:311
msgid "Improvements for working with customers"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/introduction/otrs.xml:315
msgid ""
"Added dynamic field support for customer users and customers. This makes it "
"possible to attach additional data fields to customer users and customers "
"(companies) without making manual changes to the database."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/introduction/otrs.xml:320
msgid ""
"Modernized the OTRS address book. It is now possible to search for all "
"configured custom user and customer fields."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/introduction/otrs.xml:325
msgid ""
"Added the Customer User Information Center frontend. This works like the "
"existing Customer Information Center, but focuses on all data of one "
"particular customer user, rather than a complete customer (company)."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
