#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2858
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3035
msgid ""
"<literal>SenderType</literal> defines the sender type of the article. "
"Possible values: agent, system, customer."
