#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2863
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3040
msgid ""
"<literal>IsVisibleForCustomer</literal> defines if the article should be "
"displayed in the customer interface."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2866
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3043
msgid ""
"<literal>CommunicationChannel</literal> defines the type of the article to "
