#. type: Content of: <section><para>
#: en/content/administration/dynamicfields-configuration.xml:10
msgid ""
"Please note that dynamic fields for customer users and companies need to be "
"configured accordingly in the CustomerUser and CustomerCompany mapping, "
"usually to find in <filename>Kernel/Config.pm</filename> of your OTRS "
"installation.  Examples for configuring them can be found in "
"<filename>Kernel/Config/Defaults.pm</filename>."
