"<graphic fileref=\"screenshots/appointment-calendar/calendaroverview-"
"appointmenteditrecurrence.png\" scalefit=\"1\" width=\"100%\" contentdepth="
"\"100%\"></graphic>"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/appointment-calendar/usage.xml:434
msgid ""
"After the selection is finished, it's necessary to define the runtime of the "
"recurrences. It's possible to choose either a date to repeat until, or an "
"amount of times to repeat."
